          <name>Introduced in Senate</name>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>PCAOB Enforcement Transparency Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Sarbanes-Oxley Act of 2002 to make Public Company Accounting Oversight Board disciplinary proceedings open to the public unless the board, on its own motion or after considering the motion of a party, orders otherwise.</p>]]></text>
